\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"optimize meta descriptions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=169881\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:472:\"<p>Would you like to know how to use a meta description generator in WordPress? Crafting optimized meta descriptions is essential to SEO and conversion rate optimization (CRO). Because of this, you must invest time, effort, and resources to ensure yours&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\">How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14612:\"<ul></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Would you like to know how to use a meta description generator in WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Crafting optimized meta descriptions is essential to SEO and conversion rate optimization (CRO). Because of this, you must invest time, effort, and resources to ensure yours does the job of boosting your SEO and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">clickthrough rates</a> (CTR).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to use a meta description generator in WordPress so you can save time and boost your search rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-meta-descriptions\">What are Meta Descriptions?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress\">How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-create-an-openai-account-and-generate-an-api-key\">Step 2. Create an OpenAI Account and Generate an API Key</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-connect-your-openai-account-with-aioseo\">Step 3. Connect Your OpenAI Account with AIOSEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-generate-meta-descriptions\">Step 4: Generate Meta Descriptions</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-are-meta-descriptions\">What are Meta Descriptions?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Meta descriptions are the short snippets of text that appear below the page title on search listings that appear on search engine results pages (SERPs). They summarize what a page is about, which can significantly attract clicks and boost search engine rankings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, meta descriptions also help search engines know what your page is about, leading to better indexing and ranking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore, you must <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\" title=\"How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR &amp; Rankings)\">craft optimized meta descriptions</a> to improve your chances of ranking high on SERPs.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one way to do that is to use a meta description generator.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress\">How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to boost your search rankings by using a meta description generator in WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s get to it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step to using a meta description generator in WordPress is to install and activate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best SEO plugins on the market and has a meta description generator.\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs) and drive relevant traffic to their sites. This is because the plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most beloved features in AIOSEO is the brand-new <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\" title=\"Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!\">AI Title/Description Generator</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This revolutionary module Uses <strong>ChatGPT</strong> to generate optimized meta descriptions for your posts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-2-create-an-openai-account-and-generate-an-api-key\">Step 2. Create an OpenAI Account and Generate an API Key</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To use the AI Title/Description Generator, you must first create an OpenAI account. Doing so enables you to generate an API key to link your AIOSEO account to OpenAI.&nbsp; OpenAI is the company behind ChatGPT.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you don’t have an OpenAI account yet, head over to <a href=\"https://openai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"OpenAI\">OpenAI</a>, click <strong>Get Started</strong>, and follow the steps to creating an account.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"496\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register.png\" alt=\"To get started, create an OpenAI account.\" class=\"wp-image-169885\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register-300x212.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register-600x424.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register-85x60.png 85w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-openai-register-127x90.png 127w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your account is created, click on your profile and click on view API keys on the drop-down menu.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"522\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys.png\" alt=\"Click the view API keys link to create a unique API key.\" class=\"wp-image-169886\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys-300x223.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys-600x446.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys-81x60.png 81w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-view-api-keys-121x90.png 121w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This will open a page where you can generate your API key. To do that, click on the <strong>Create new secret key</strong> button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key.png\" alt=\"Click the Create new secret keybutton.\" class=\"wp-image-169887\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key-300x180.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key-600x361.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key-100x60.png 100w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-create-api-key-150x90.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>OpenAI will then generate an API key for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1.jpeg\" alt=\"Copy the generated API key. \" class=\"wp-image-169889\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1.jpeg 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-300x207.jpeg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-600x415.jpeg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-87x60.jpeg 87w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-130x90.jpeg 130w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Copy the API key by clicking on the green “copy” button next to the API key.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-3-connect-your-openai-account-with-aioseo\">Step 3. Connect Your OpenAI Account with AIOSEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have generated and copied your API key, head to your site and open a page or post in editor mode. Next, scroll down to the AIOSEO meta box, where you’ll find our brand new robot button inside the <strong>Post Title</strong> and <strong>Meta Description</strong> boxes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"353\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png\" alt=\"Click the Robot button, and a modal will open, asking you to paste your API key.\" class=\"wp-image-165754\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click the <strong>Robot</strong> button, and a modal will open, asking you to paste your API key.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1.png\" alt=\"Paste your API key\" class=\"wp-image-169892\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-300x175.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-600x350.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-api-key-1-154x90.png 154w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve pasted your API key, click the <strong>Connect</strong> button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"358\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1.jpeg\" alt=\"Click the Connect button\" class=\"wp-image-169893\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1.jpeg 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1-300x153.jpeg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1-600x306.jpeg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1-118x60.jpeg 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/meta-description-generator-paste-api-key-1-176x90.jpeg 176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And that’s it! You can now use the AI-powered meta description generator to craft optimized meta descriptions and post titles.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-4-generate-meta-descriptions\">Step 4: Generate Meta Descriptions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After connecting your OpenAI account to AIOSEO, you can now use the meta description generator. To do this, click the <strong>Robot</strong> button in the AIOSEO meta box. The AI Title/Description generator will then scan your content and offer 5 suggestions based on the main theme of your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/inBzExEB38ENl__y25accfMr6Y_O_tEGI5e7QzBZCtk3TEusTjWFJflU3JyM6zpuiWjVC6hu_RM5gnp8o7qpH4jlNBOJOAfvOBR4WiEbvEO7Oo3_X9qlQwCoovhrfFPPPmWFmAhiI_oTQFcLTKKvWqY\" alt=\"OpenAI will generate 5 meta description examples for you to choose from. \"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Select the one you want by clicking on the <strong>+</strong> button. Next, tweak and refine it according to your taste.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And that’s it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ve used a meta description generator to boost your search engine rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn how to use a meta description generator to boost your search engine rankings. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\" title=\"The 6 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023\">best AI SEO tools for WordPress</a> and our tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-emojis-to-your-wordpress-blog/\" title=\"How to Add Emojis to Your WordPress Blog (Super Easy)\">adding emojis in meta descriptions</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\">How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:202:\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 17:30:48 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=168649\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:497:\"<p>At AIOSEO, we are always looking for ways to improve our product and make SEO easier for everyone. Last week we announced our brand new OpenAI integration to help you generate high-quality SEO titles and meta descriptions. And just like&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\">Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5922:\"<p>At AIOSEO, we are always looking for ways to improve our product and make SEO easier for everyone. Last week we <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/dominate-search-rankings-with-aioseos-ai-title-description-generator/\" title=\"Dominate Search Rankings with AIOSEO’s AI Title/Description Generator\">announced our brand new OpenAI integration</a> to help you generate high-quality SEO titles and meta descriptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And just like that, we&#8217;ve made it even better!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We listened to your feedback and heard that you wanted to get <strong>better results at a lower cost</strong>. Today I&#8217;m happy to announce that as of AIOSEO Pro 4.3.3, we made the switch to <strong>ChatGPT</strong> for our AI Title/Description Generator.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Switching to ChatGPT will provide better results at a fraction of the cost! The new API is 10x cheaper than the original Davinci model.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With the integration of ChatGPT, we are confident that you will be able to generate SEO metadata even more efficiently and effectively than before and rank higher in search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what does this mean for you? Let&#8217;s dive in&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Easily Craft High-Quality Post Titles and Meta Descriptions</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With this latest update, <strong>nothing changes for you at all</strong>. Our brand new AI Title/Description Generator still takes the labor out of crafting post titles and meta descriptions, and all with just the click of a button!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"353\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-165754\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Simply click on the robot icon that&#8217;s embedded in the <strong>Post Title</strong> and <strong>Meta Description</strong> fields. The integration with OpenAI will take it the rest of the way and generate 5 high-quality suggestions based on your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s an example where we generated suggestions for our post about adding box shadows in WordPress:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"378\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-165755\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results.jpeg 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-300x162.jpeg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-600x324.jpeg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-111x60.jpeg 111w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-167x90.jpeg 167w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After that, just click on the plus button to add your preferred suggestion directly to the SEO meta fields.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"168\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-165756\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2.jpeg 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2-300x72.jpeg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2-600x144.jpeg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2-190x46.jpeg 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-2-374x90.jpeg 374w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can always edit the suggestion afterward if you need to adjust it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Transform Your SEO Strategy with the AI Title/Description Generator</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With our new AI Title/Description Generator, generating engaging SEO post titles and meta descriptions is just a click away! This powerful tool saves you time and ensures that your metadata is optimized for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For those with a lot of content to update, manually updating post titles and meta descriptions on hundreds of pages can be daunting. But with our new AI Title/Description Generator, this task is accomplished effortlessly and efficiently, providing you with optimized content that has a better chance of ranking higher and generating more clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#8217;t miss out on this essential tool for your SEO needs. Check out our product <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/changelog/\" title=\"AIOSEO Changelog\">changelog</a> to see the other notable improvements we&#8217;ve made to many features you love.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a reminder, our ChatGPT OpenAI integration is available in AIOSEO Pro 4.3.3. We encourage all our users to upgrade today and take advantage of this fantastic feature.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are committed to providing our users with the best possible service, and this change is just one example of how we are continuously working to improve our product.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thank you for choosing AIOSEO for your SEO needs. We look forward to helping you succeed in your online endeavors!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>-Benjamin Rojas (President of AIOSEO).</em></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\">Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{