:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:428:\"<p>Looking for the best AI SEO tools for WordPress? Artificial intelligence (AI) and many other facets of the current digital revolution have resulted in a new crop of tools that can reduce the time required to perform certain tasks. One&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\">The 7 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22312:\"<p>Looking for the best AI SEO tools for WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI) and many other facets of the current digital revolution have resulted in a new crop of tools that can reduce the time required to perform certain tasks. One industry that has benefitted from these technological advancements is the SEO industry.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why AI SEO tools are fast becoming the future of WordPress search engine optimization.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you some of the best AI SEO tools for your WordPress site.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-ai-seo-tools\">What are AI SEO tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress-our-expert-picks\">The Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress: Our Expert Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-link-whisper\">2. Link Whisper</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-surferseo\">3. SurferSEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-frase\">4. Frase</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-wordlift\">5. WordLift</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-seopress\">6. SEOPress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-rank-math\">7. Rank Math</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress-our-top-pick\">The Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress: Our Top Pick</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-are-ai-seo-tools\">What are AI SEO tools?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>AI SEO tools use artificial intelligence (AI) to improve your workflow and efficiency when working on SEO-related tasks. Because they speed up the execution of tasks and improve efficiency, they help improve your rankings. As a result, your site will enjoy a greater influx of high-quality traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the aspects AI SEO tools help you with include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Content creation and optimization</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Site analytics and optimization</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Market analysis</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content planning and keyword research</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The best AI SEO tools are easy to use and have excellent customer support. And for small businesses, they should come with an affordable price tag.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress-our-expert-picks\">The Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress: Our Expert Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to supercharge your SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s our expertly curated list of the best AI SEO tools to help you do that.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best AI SEO tools for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of smart business owners and marketers use it to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their sites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many small business owners and SEOs love AIOSEO because it has powerful features that help make SEO super easy. And some of them are powered by AI. We’ll look at 2 examples:</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-ai-title-description-generator\">AI Title/Description Generator</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/dominate-search-rankings-with-aioseos-ai-title-description-generator/\" title=\"[NEW] Dominate Search Rankings with AIOSEO’s AI Title/Description Generator\">AI Title/Description Generator</a> helps take the labor out of crafting post titles and meta descriptions as it automatically does this at a click of a button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"353\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s AI Title/Description Generator is a powerful AI tool to help automate meta data writing.\" class=\"wp-image-165754\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1.png 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/seo-title-generator-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The AI engine then creates 5 suggestions based on your content…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"378\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results.jpeg\" alt=\"The AI Title/Description Generator gives you 5 suggestions.\" class=\"wp-image-165755\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results.jpeg 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-300x162.jpeg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-600x324.jpeg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-111x60.jpeg 111w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/post-title-generator-results-167x90.jpeg 167w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All you need to do is select the one you want and tweak it if necessary.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With optimized SEO post titles and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">meta descriptions</a>, your content will:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Rank higher on search engines</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gain more visibility on SERPs</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drive more traffic to your site</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And all it takes to gain these results is a simple click of a button!</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-link-assistant\">Link Assistant</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Another AI-powered feature <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">Link Assistant</a>, our AI-powered internal link building module.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">automates internal link building</a> by crawling your site to check for internal linking opportunities. The Overview shows you the number of external and internal links and the affiliate links on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"329\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant.png\" alt=\"Link Assistant is a handy feature that helps build internal links and boost yourSEO.\" class=\"wp-image-87481\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant-600x282.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also get a more detailed report of the links on your site by clicking on the <strong>Links Report</strong>. It then gives you a report with <strong>Linking Suggestions</strong> and shows you the <strong>Orphan Posts</strong> on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png\" alt=\"Link Assistant is a powerful tool that can help boost your internal linking strategy.\" class=\"wp-image-79017\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is that you don’t even have to open the target page to add the suggested links. Instead, simply open the <strong>Links Report</strong> and click on a post or page. Doing so will open a window with internal inbound and internal outbound link suggestions.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"316\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link.png\" alt=\"You can automatically add internal links using Link Assistant.\" class=\"wp-image-167487\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link-300x135.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link-600x270.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link-133x60.png 133w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/link-assistant-adding-link-200x90.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This level of automation just makes the internal linking process faster and more efficient.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re looking for the best AI SEO tool for WordPress, then look no further than AIOSEO. Because it’s an easy-to-use plugin, you don’t need any coding or technical knowledge to use it to its full potential.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $49.60. A free plan is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-link-whisper\">2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/linkwhisper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Link Whisper\">Link Whisper</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/linkwhisper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper.png\" alt=\"Link Whisper home page.\" class=\"wp-image-167488\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-300x120.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-600x240.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-150x60.png 150w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-225x90.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/linkwhisper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Link Whisper\">Link Whisper</a> is an AI-powered WordPress plugin designed to help you build strategic internal links. The plugin scans your draft in WordPress, finds relevant <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"Posts vs. Pages in WordPress — Everything You Need to Know\">posts and pages</a> on your site, and generates a list of suggestions for internal linking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like AIOSEO, the plugin displays suggested places to link to complete with editable anchor text. This enables you to automatically add internal links without opening the page in editor mode.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $77 for a single-site license.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-surferseo\">3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/surferseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Surfer SEO\">SurferSEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/surferseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo.png\" alt=\"Surfer SEO home page\" class=\"wp-image-167491\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo-300x129.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo-600x258.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo-140x60.png 140w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-surfer-seo-209x90.png 209w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/surfer-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Surfer SEO\">Surfer SEO</a> is an AI-powered on-page optimization tool that helps users ensure their content is primed for better ranking on search engine results pages (SERPs). The tool compares and analyzes top-ranking content on SERPs and gives you a report of the keywords you need to include in your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides content optimization, SurferSEO also generates outlines and content briefs optimized for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. Paid plans start at $49/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-frase\">4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase.png\" alt=\"Frase is a powerful AI-powered content optimization tool.\" class=\"wp-image-170958\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-600x278.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-130x60.png 130w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-194x90.png 194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a> is a powerful AI SEO tool designed to make content creation easy. It automatically generates SEO-friendly content briefs by crawling the web and compiling the top results. It also helps you optimize your content by comparing it to top-ranking content for your keyword. The tool then gives you a score and recommendations for improving your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your content is live, Frase also gives you an analytics report of your content&#8217;s performance. This is essential in helping you curb content decay.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $14.99/month. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-wordlift\">5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordlift/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"WordLift\">WordLift</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordlift/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift.png\" alt=\"WordLift home page\" class=\"wp-image-167492\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-wordlift-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordlift/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"WordLift\">Wordlift</a> is another AI SEO tool to consider for your WordPress site. It automatically adds structured data to your website so search engines can better understand your content. This also helps search engines generate a knowledge graph about your brand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other functions of WordLift include analyzing your content, classifying words into entities, and generating recommendations for optimizing your content. It also suggests images for your content, helps with internal linking, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: €49/month (billed annually)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-seopress\">6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seopress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"SEOPress\">SEOPress</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seopress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"354\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress.png\" alt=\"SEOPress home page\" class=\"wp-image-167493\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-seopress-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/seopress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"SEOPress\">SEOPress</a> is another WordPress SEO plugin powered by AI. The plugin&#8217;s straightforward setup makes it a great option for beginners. However, seasoned users will also find advanced controls to help them fine-tune their SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEOPress has most of the features you’ll find in some of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\" title=\"8 Best SEO Plugins for WordPress in 2023 (Tried and Tested)\">best WordPress SEO plugins</a>. Examples include open graph support, image and content XML sitemaps, redirects, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $49/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-6-rank-math\">7. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Rank Math\">Rank Math</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"284\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath.png\" alt=\"Rank Math home page\" class=\"wp-image-167494\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-300x122.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-600x243.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-148x60.png 148w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-222x90.png 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Rank Math\">Rank Math</a> is another WordPress SEO plugin with AI-powered features to help automate SEO tasks and increase efficiency.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like AIOSEO, the plugin has an internal linking feature. However, Rank Math’s link builder isn’t automatic. It’s manual. Linking suggestions are shown in your WordPress content editor, and then you have to manually copy the suggested link and insert it into your text.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin also has other SEO features like a schema generator, redirection manager, local SEO module, etc.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $59/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress-our-top-pick\">The Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress: Our Top Pick</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is our top pick for the best AI SEO tool for WordPress. One reason is it’s a powerful plugin that’s super easy to use, making it an indispensable SEO tool. Plus, it has a feature set that enables you to DIY most aspects of your SEO so you can compete with big brands in your space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best AI SEO tool for your site. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\" title=\"How to Start a Small Business Blog in 2023\">how to start a small business blog</a> or our tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-local-business-schema-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add Local Business Schema in WordPress\">adding Local Business schema in WordPress.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\">The 7 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">A